# Title: Potential PowerShell Obfuscation Using Character Join
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-01-09
# Level: low
# Description: Detects specific techniques often seen used inside of PowerShell scripts to obfscuate Alias creation
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.execution, attack.t1027, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_susp_alias_obfscuation.yml

ScriptBlockText="*-Alias*" ScriptBlockText="* -Value (-join(*"